{"tid":2424601,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【超高質本土音樂mv】只要有人繼承，真相和良知會永存","createTime":"2021-02-26T16:50:07.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-27T06:48:40.000Z","uid":263423,"like":13,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"6b1c8e163940bae7427570cd9231028decb6b0e0","tid":2424601,"uid":263423,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-26T16:50:07.000Z","msg":"<strong>The hertz - 千世書</strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/rqKxbmXBbD0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FrqKxbmXBbD0&d=FFizHFgeJnC1szROyuQz%2B0zlOXIvf7DEkQzrkg%2FJo1w%3D&h=1033e64b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/rqKxbmXBbD0</a><br />\n正撚到仆街！！無人講我講<br />\n<br />\n留意左The hertz好耐<br />\n音樂同mv都做得好好 好有風格<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我呢啲普通聽眾都知<br />\n佢咁樣做啲特別主題、玩風格係一個大風險嚟<br />\n會承受難推廣/中意嘅好中意 唔中意嘅好唔中意嘅挑戰<br />\n所以我特別欣賞HZ仲成日創新、重本（畢竟情情愛愛呢啲主題最受歡迎、最穩陣大家都知）<br />\n希望開po令大家都注意到呢隊咁值得欣賞嘅樂隊！<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"red\">依家有良知 肯創新嘅樂隊、藝人已經好少<br />\n如果大家聽左/睇左中意嘅文化野可以share出去<br />\n唔好怕煩到人 好野緊係一齊分享～<br />\n希望香港個本土文創圏可以活躍翻！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span>"},{"pid":"2bc17316acfe720bb70ca45f9bae4e45952e6b2b","tid":2424601,"uid":226955,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-26T16:51:08.000Z","msg":"Push <img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/yea.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"06966004df93a22aa5e8c94ed395065b99bca860","tid":2424601,"uid":263423,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-26T16:51:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />自推幾下先"},{"pid":"7811ee81e32c61dafa57749fdb06f6dd2552fa11","tid":2424601,"uid":263423,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2bc17316acfe720bb70ca45f9bae4e45952e6b2b","tid":2424601,"uid":226955,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-26T16:51:08.000Z","msg":"Push <img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/yea.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" 